Capital Shopping Centers Names Butterworth as Operating Chief

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-09-26T09:35:13Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-26/capital-shopping-centers-names-butterworth-as-operating-chief.html
Capital Shopping Centres Group Plc (CSCG) 
said it appointed Mike Butterworth as chief operating officer
after Kay Chaldecott quit as a director after 27 years with the
company.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
 vwessels@bloomberg.net  